=== Noun ===
'''building''' (''[[countable]] and [[uncountable]]''; ''plural'' '''buildings''')

#(''uncountable'') The action of [[build]]ing.
#(''countable'') An [[edifice]] that is in the process of being built.
#(''countable'') An edifice (usually one that isn't ruined).

